        <item>
            <title>【教学】AI 帮你自制 WhatsApp Sticker，由想 Idea 至生成图片、汇入 WhatsApp 教学</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 12:02:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303155</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ChatGPT 早前升级了 GPT-4o 图片生成功能，推出「创作图像」功能，让用家可以生成各种不同风格如漫画、吉卜力风格等的图片。现时我们也可以透过其「创作图像」功能，轻松制作有自己、亲友样子的贴图。以下小编将会和大家分享如何使用 ChatGPT 帮你自动生成 WhatsApp 贴图。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303243" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可生成各种风格的个人 sticker</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可在 WhatsApp 上使用</p><h2>需求</h2><p>ChatGPT 帐户（免费每日仅可生成 3 张，因此建议订阅 Pro 或 Plus ）</p><p>VPN（香港用户需要 VPN 方可使用到 ChatGPT，台湾则不需要）</p><p>WhatsApp（贴图也可汇出到 LINE 拍贴应用程式）</p><h2>Step 1 使用 ChatGPT「创作图像」</h2><p>开启 VPN 后，登入 ChatGPT 帐户，开启一个新对话，选择「创作图像」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1.jpg 968w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「创作图像」</p><br /><b>
根据图片人物衣著、外貌特征，生成 3 张美少女战士式风格方形贴图，人物表情需要为开怀大笑、愤怒和肚饿。</p><p>输入好指令之后就可以点击发送，稍后片刻待 ChatGPT 帮你生成贴图。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303200" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755.jpg 885w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> ▲上传图片并输入指令</p><p>不消一阵 ChatGPT 就可帮你生成 3 张方形的图片。你可以要求 ChatGPT 帮你再修改贴图，小编想 ChatGPT 重新绘画肚饿，因为贴图看起来与愤怒无异。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809-559x580.jpg" alt="" width="559" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809-559x580.jpg 559w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809.jpg 867w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 559px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904-507x580.jpg" alt="" width="507" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904-507x580.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904.jpg 786w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 507px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲生成了 3 张图片，但愤怒和肚饿看起来都一样</p><p>小编输入指令「肚饿看起来与愤怒差不多，请更改肚饿图，使主角看起来肚饿而不是愤怒。」稍等一阵 ChatGPT 就可更新贴图。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231-563x580.jpg" alt="" width="563" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231-563x580.jpg 563w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231.jpg 713w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 563px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲已更新贴图</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Step 3 加上文字</h2><p>现在你可以输入指令：「在 3 张贴图上面加上文字效果」，不过由于小编曾要求 ChatGPT 更改肚饿版本贴图，因此就加入了一句「请使用最新版本的肚饿」。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129-477x580.jpg" alt="" width="477" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129-477x580.jpg 477w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129.jpg 740w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 477px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加入了文字的 Sticker</p><h2>Step 4 加入更多细节</h2><p>你可以要求 ChatGPT 帮你润饰贴图，例如加入更多细节。首先点击图片，在绿色栏输入你的要求。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4-628x580.jpg" alt="" width="628" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4-628x580.jpg 628w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4.jpg 975w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 628px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在绿色栏输入你的要求</p><p>小编使用指令如下：请加入一个思想气泡，气泡内有一碗饭</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055.jpg 801w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在绿色栏输入你的要求</p><p>不消一阵 ChatGPT 就按照我要求加入了一碗饭。你可以要求 ChatGPT 加入更多细节，你的贴图就会更精致。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301-588x580.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301-588x580.jpg 588w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301.jpg 813w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 588px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新增了一碗饭</p><p>下面是小编要求 ChatGPT 加入更多细节的图片，指令可参考图片下方说明：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲请加入一个思想气泡，气泡内有一碗饭</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在背景加入大量卡通柴犬、可爱小猫小狗，显示主角真的很开心</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在背景加入蘑菇云爆炸效果，显示图中主角真的很愤怒</p><h2>Step 5 下载图片</h2><p>现在就可以下载你的贴图。移动滑鼠至图片上即可见到「下载」按键。点击即可下载</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3.jpg 888w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击即可下载</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>不过要留意，偶尔 ChatGPT 生成的中文会怪怪的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「肚饿到晕」的「饿」和「晕」有点怪</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
